df.dropna(inplace=True)

groups = dict(list(df_grouped))
dfs = [df for df in groups.values()]
max_freqs = [384363.5]*15
#max_freqs=[384178.599, 384179.091, 384184.733]
zipped_data = list(zip(dfs, max_freqs))
fig, ax = plt.subplots()
for i, (df, max_freq)  in enumerate(zipped_data[:]):
    data = df.dropna()
    freqs = ((max_freq-PUMP_FREQUENCY)-(data['tempV']-data['tempV'].min())*FREQVSVOLT- (data['currV']-data['currV'].min())*FREQVSCURR)
    ax=plot_spline_fit(ax, x=freqs, y=data['ratio'], yerr=data['ratioErr'],scolor=f'C{i}', mfc=f'C{i}',color=f'C{i}', s=0.0, ms=5, figsize=(10, 10), label=f"CAT Amplituide = { df.iloc[10]['cat_AOM_ampl'] :.2f}", linewidth=2.5)

plt.legend()

plt.savefig(os.path.join(MEASURE_FOLDER, 'lossFeatures.png'))

y = 1 - data['ratio'].values
x = freqs

y = [b for (a,b) in sorted(zip(x,y), key=lambda pair: pair[0])]
x = sorted(x)

y = y[:-13]
x = x[:-13]
model = GaussianModel(prefix='peak_')
params = model.make_params(amplitude=0.4, center=-49.2, sigma=1)

knot_xvals = np.concatenate((np.linspace(-51.63, -50.5, 5), np.linspace(-49, -47.89, 5))) 

bkg = SplineModel(prefix='bkg_', xknots=knot_xvals)
params.update(bkg.guess(y, x))

model = model + bkg

params['peak_amplitude'].min = 0
params['peak_center'].min = -50
params['peak_center'].max = -49

out = model.fit(y, params, x=x)
print(out.fit_report())

comps = out.eval_components()
plt.plot(x, y, 'ro', label='data')
plt.plot(x, out.best_fit, 'bo', label='best fit')
# plt.plot(x, comps['bkg_'], label='background')
# plt.plot(x, comps['peak_'], label='peak')
plt.legend()
knot_yvals = np.array([o.value for o in out.params.values() if o.name.startswith('bkg')])
plt.plot(knot_xvals, knot_yvals, 'o', color='black', label='spline knots values')
